    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Pattern having the appearance of fine lines. An example is decoration done entirely of fine wire, chiefly to ornament gold and silver, or as openwork made of wire.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
